    <h1>Endangered Animals</h1>

    <h2>American Bison</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Scientific Name:</strong> Bison bison</li>
        <li><strong>Where it lives:</strong> North America (primarily in the United States)</li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Endangered</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>California Condor</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Scientific Name:</strong> Gymnogyps californianus</li>
        <li><strong>Where it lives:</strong> Western United States, Baja California in Mexico</li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Endangered</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Florida Panther</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Scientific Name:</strong> Puma concolor coryi</li>
        <li><strong>Where it lives:</strong> Southern Florida, USA</li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Threatened</li>
    </ul>

